1
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:44,450
Sanzhou press

2
00:01:50,180 --> 00:01:53,610
Didn't Editor.Yu use to work for them?

3
00:01:56,240 --> 00:02:00,090
They also pressed your first animations

4
00:02:02,420 --> 00:02:03,570
What a coincidence

5
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,830
And you know what

6
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:09,720
The former chief editor of Sanzhou Press is

7
00:02:10,010 --> 00:02:11,300
Gu Yishan's uncle

8
00:02:12,340 --> 00:02:17,180
Xiang Zeyi’s stolen animations were also handled by them

9
00:02:19,530 --> 00:02:22,200
Do you think Editor Yu know about this?

10
00:02:23,300 --> 00:02:25,590
She did work there for a long time

11
00:02:28,110 --> 00:02:30,460
She might  have something we don't know

12
00:02:33,230 --> 00:02:37,840
[21.I want a home, a place that belongs to us]

13
00:02:48,790 --> 00:02:50,860
Mrs Yu, do you still remember this book?

14
00:02:51,980 --> 00:02:56,680
My press was about to publish it, of course I remember

15
00:02:56,830 --> 00:02:59,950
So you know exactly what happened

16
00:03:00,670 --> 00:03:02,000
I heard that

17
00:03:02,890 --> 00:03:07,150
The author Gu Yishan is the nephew of our chief editor

18
00:03:07,300 --> 00:03:13,740
At that time a student at School of Fine Art hurt him accidentally and got into jail for that

19
00:03:14,790 --> 00:03:16,690
What a pity

20
00:03:17,130 --> 00:03:21,520
Mrs Yu, do you know other things about that?

21
00:03:23,570 --> 00:03:27,210
Yezi, why do you want to know about that?

22
00:03:29,810 --> 00:03:33,640
That student means a lot to me

23
00:03:37,110 --> 00:03:39,920
Xiang Zeyi, is this his name?

24
00:03:39,940 --> 00:03:40,440
Yes

25
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:48,470
His style is very unique and it impressed us a lot

26
00:03:48,640 --> 00:03:54,990
But when we asked him for finished animations, it was Gu Yishan who brought them over

27
00:03:56,470 --> 00:03:58,390
How could it prove that Xiang Zeyi was the writer?

28
00:04:00,710 --> 00:04:06,260
Mrs Yu, did we all miss any details? This really means a lot to Xiang Zeyi

29
00:04:08,090 --> 00:04:10,890
Yezi, it's been so long

30
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:14,980
Gu Yishan is still in a coma and Sanzhou Press has already closed

31
00:04:16,420 --> 00:04:18,530
I can do nothing for you about that

32
00:04:31,730 --> 00:04:34,180
In those years Xiang Zeyi went to...

33
00:04:36,020 --> 00:04:42,690
If it wasn’t for Mr.Jingshang to tell us everything, we wouldn’t know at all

34
00:04:46,190 --> 00:04:48,970
When did Yezi know?

35
00:04:50,530 --> 00:04:51,500
Long time ago

36
00:04:54,580 --> 00:04:58,310
Because Xiang Zeyi told her all

37
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:07,910
Daniao told me that Xiang was wronged for copying so he’d go to reason things out

38
00:05:09,030 --> 00:05:10,830
But they got into fighting

39
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:14,230
Xiang was meant to self-defend and pushed him

40
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:21,070
It was just bad luck, not his fault

41
00:05:23,930 --> 00:05:27,090
Yes, Xiang Zeyi is also a victim

42
00:05:31,050 --> 00:05:36,450
I agree but he did go into jail

43
00:05:37,860 --> 00:05:40,550
We do trust him but what about others?

44
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:45,100
We can't ensure that others don't judge him

45
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,650
What to do then?

46
00:05:48,610 --> 00:05:51,390
Yezi really has a struggling love life

47
00:05:54,590 --> 00:05:58,380
Anyways, everything is gonna be fine

48
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:04,100
I believe Yezi can handle it well

49
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:17,980
Doctor, how is my nephew?

50
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:22,250
His congestion in head transferred and it caused this danger

51
00:06:23,270 --> 00:06:28,820
Which also gave us a chance to cure his brain

52
00:06:29,420 --> 00:06:31,700
You mean...

53
00:06:32,700 --> 00:06:33,770
You can call it a miracle

54
00:06:34,710 --> 00:06:39,070
If nothing goes wrong, he’ll wake up after the anesthetic

55
00:06:40,660 --> 00:06:42,960
Great! Thank you doctor

56
00:07:03,970 --> 00:07:06,440
Doctor said he'll wake up soon

57
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:15,660
His family are here, they can’t be happy to see me

58
00:07:19,870 --> 00:07:23,220
He is coming to himself, go and tell Yezi

59
00:07:57,910 --> 00:07:58,410
Auntie

60
00:07:59,390 --> 00:08:00,380
Sen

61
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:05,760
I’m making you red-cooked pork tomorrow, remember to come over

62
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:07,200
Tomorrow?

63
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:09,570
Auntie, you told me to come the day after tomorrow earlier today

64
00:08:13,110 --> 00:08:14,750
Did I say so?

65
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:21,380
OK then, remember to come over the day after tomorrow

66
00:08:21,610 --> 00:08:22,790
I will be there

67
00:08:23,810 --> 00:08:24,640
See you then

68
00:08:47,950 --> 00:08:48,450
Hello

69
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:52,760
Auntie, tomorrow we are having a physical examination for family

70
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:55,790
I’ll come and pick you up in the morning

71
00:08:57,420 --> 00:09:00,470
No need to bother you

72
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:03,420
No bother at all. It's benefits of the hospital, we might as well use it

73
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,880
It’s a deal, I’ll be there tomorrow morning

74
00:09:07,930 --> 00:09:10,210
Fine, see you tomorrow

75
00:09:13,250 --> 00:09:14,010
What a nice boy

76
00:09:27,620 --> 00:09:28,280
Doctor Lin

77
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:32,240
Auntie, sit

78
00:09:34,670 --> 00:09:37,010
I hate to bother you

79
00:09:37,100 --> 00:09:41,140
You see,all these blood test and CT lasted all morning

80
00:09:42,010 --> 00:09:45,250
I told you auntie, it’s benefits of the hospital

81
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:48,100
You are such a sweet kid

82
00:09:49,030 --> 00:09:51,370
What about the result?

83
00:09:52,450 --> 00:09:54,520
We need to wait for a couple of days

84
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:56,350
But I've asked about it, nothing serious

85
00:09:56,870 --> 00:09:57,930
Good

86
00:09:58,860 --> 00:10:00,700
I'm getting old and physical examination worries me

87
00:10:00,900 --> 00:10:02,550
Yezi used to handle it for me

88
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:05,380
She was more nervous than me when waiting for the results

89
00:10:05,890 --> 00:10:10,290
I don't worry much about myself but I hate to bother her

90
00:10:11,230 --> 00:10:14,820
Don’t tell her if there is nothing serious

91
00:10:15,270 --> 00:10:16,400
OK

92
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:18,470
Thank you Lin Sen

93
00:10:18,700 --> 00:10:19,860
I’m leaving

94
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:20,980
I’ll talk you out

95
00:10:21,030 --> 00:10:24,570
No. You’ve been working all morning

96
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,540
It’s too late for you to come over

97
00:10:39,810 --> 00:10:41,350
-I had an operation and just got off work

98
00:10:43,090 --> 00:10:44,030
My dad bought you a birthday present

99
00:10:45,210 --> 00:10:47,890
It's so nice of Uncle Lin to prepare gifts for me every year

100
00:10:48,020 --> 00:10:49,130
how can I thank him?

101
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:51,530
I’ll tell him you said thanks

102
00:10:52,830 --> 00:10:53,360
What do you want to drink?

103
00:10:53,900 --> 00:10:54,400
Water

104
00:10:55,570 --> 00:10:57,230
Same as always

105
00:11:17,250 --> 00:11:19,100
What’s wrong? Do you have something to say?

106
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,730
I've been thinking about my dad

107
00:11:23,420 --> 00:11:25,000
He'd been struggling alone in foreign countries all those years

108
00:11:25,710 --> 00:11:29,640
Only telling us good news because he didn't want his son to worry

109
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:32,840
Parents are all like that

110
00:11:33,680 --> 00:11:38,670
Yes, all parents want to play superman in front of their kids

111
00:11:39,980 --> 00:11:45,590
They play it for so long that they forget they are getting old

112
00:11:49,380 --> 00:11:50,240
They were once young

113
00:11:52,380 --> 00:11:54,690
We are used to being cared and understood by them

114
00:11:57,160 --> 00:11:58,980
But we forget to care about them

115
00:12:04,580 --> 00:12:07,920
Lin Sen, are you ok? You seem strange today

116
00:12:09,630 --> 00:12:13,480
Something happened back in hospital and I saw my dad's present for you

117
00:12:13,560 --> 00:12:14,460
Somehow I was touched

118
00:12:16,100 --> 00:12:16,820
Don’t worry too much

119
00:12:17,570 --> 00:12:20,260
Your parents are taking good care of themselves

120
00:12:20,620 --> 00:12:23,410
And you also fly over several times a year to see them

121
00:12:28,990 --> 00:12:31,950
Fine, you can rest now, I need to get back to hospital

122
00:12:32,530 --> 00:12:33,670
At this time?

123
00:12:35,420 --> 00:12:38,640
We asked some experts to come over tomorrow for a tough case

124
00:12:39,560 --> 00:12:40,970
I need to get prepared tonight

125
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:42,490
Bye

126
00:12:48,570 --> 00:12:50,950
Make more time for your parents

127
00:12:52,870 --> 00:12:53,740
They are getting old

128
00:12:55,790 --> 00:12:56,500
I know

129
00:13:01,470 --> 00:13:02,050
Good night

130
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:05,040
See you

131
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:24,580
Honey

132
00:13:33,180 --> 00:13:35,320
Honey, are you alright?

133
00:13:36,310 --> 00:13:37,200
I’m fine

134
00:13:38,110 --> 00:13:39,960
I’m going to buy you some medicine

135
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:41,430
No need

136
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:44,610
I might be tired from working. I’m gonna be fine

137
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:47,550
Get up then, the floor is cold

138
00:13:48,150 --> 00:13:50,260
Be careful

139
00:13:52,060 --> 00:13:54,100
You want some water?

140
00:13:54,880 --> 00:13:55,380
OK

141
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:05,940
Here, honey, water

142
00:14:10,750 --> 00:14:12,870
You need rest, I'll take you to bedroom

143
00:14:15,110 --> 00:14:16,440
Go to bed and have a rest

144
00:14:50,830 --> 00:14:51,770
Yezi?

145
00:14:53,700 --> 00:14:54,550
You are back

146
00:14:55,030 --> 00:14:56,880
I miss my family

147
00:14:57,860 --> 00:14:59,300
Am I not welcomed?

148
00:14:59,340 --> 00:15:01,530
Of course you are

149
00:15:01,670 --> 00:15:03,250
Come back whenever you want

150
00:15:04,530 --> 00:15:07,100
I made some pork ribs soup
I'll warm up some for you

151
00:15:10,570 --> 00:15:12,930
My mom can read my mind

152
00:15:13,100 --> 00:15:16,390
You knew I’d come back and made my favorite soup

153
00:15:17,630 --> 00:15:21,090
Go take a shower. I’ll bring the soup to your room

154
00:15:21,230 --> 00:15:21,730
OK

155
00:15:21,860 --> 00:15:22,360
Go

156
00:15:27,410 --> 00:15:27,950
Soup

157
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:34,780
If that Xiang Zeyi is ready to come back

158
00:15:35,330 --> 00:15:38,750
He should be prepared to face and handle all these troubles

159
00:15:39,490 --> 00:15:43,010
Including the current situation, shouldn’t he?

160
00:15:47,570 --> 00:15:48,590
I can’t understand why

161
00:15:50,300 --> 00:15:52,740
every time when I think my chance has come

162
00:15:54,050 --> 00:15:54,690
It disappears

163
00:15:55,620 --> 00:15:57,470
Does god just love to play me around?

164
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:01,690
God is busy enough with his own business

165
00:16:05,310 --> 00:16:10,090
What we need to figure out is what we really want

166
00:16:10,620 --> 00:16:14,380
And try to do what we can do and we should do

167
00:16:14,870 --> 00:16:15,460
That’s enough

168
00:16:19,930 --> 00:16:24,190
You are smart enough to understand what I’m saying

169
00:16:27,820 --> 00:16:30,130
You barely say good things about me

170
00:16:32,680 --> 00:16:35,740
I barely say good things about anyone

171
00:16:37,340 --> 00:16:38,370
Cherish your turn

172
00:16:51,060 --> 00:16:51,580
Hello

173
00:17:00,520 --> 00:17:03,650
Hello, I am Yezi’s father

174
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:05,790
Uncle, nice to meet you

175
00:17:06,550 --> 00:17:07,400
Walk with me

176
00:17:12,080 --> 00:17:13,670
When Yezi was a little girl

177
00:17:13,950 --> 00:17:17,380
She used to walk with me around the park every morning

178
00:17:18,340 --> 00:17:19,820
Like what you’re doing now

179
00:17:20,930 --> 00:17:25,570
I can’t remember when it’s only me walking

180
00:17:27,420 --> 00:17:27,920
Uncle

181
00:17:29,640 --> 00:17:33,290
Yezi shas been busy lately

182
00:17:33,980 --> 00:17:36,870
But I believe she still thinks about you

183
00:17:38,250 --> 00:17:38,960
I know

184
00:17:39,650 --> 00:17:42,720
My girl looks strong

185
00:17:43,860 --> 00:17:47,010
She just doesn’t want show people her weakness

186
00:17:47,570 --> 00:17:48,940
She only tells us good news

187
00:17:49,630 --> 00:17:52,610
Her heart is soft like her mother

188
00:17:55,850 --> 00:17:58,690
You spend a lot of time together

189
00:17:59,380 --> 00:18:00,180
But to be honest

190
00:18:01,710 --> 00:18:04,910
I know Yezi better than you do

191
00:18:05,350 --> 00:18:06,580
After all, she is my daughter

192
00:18:07,750 --> 00:18:09,410
I witnessed her growth

193
00:18:11,270 --> 00:18:14,680
The reason why I called you here is to talk

194
00:18:14,970 --> 00:18:17,250
And to see if two men who know Yezi the most

195
00:18:17,660 --> 00:18:20,960
Share the same thoughts on some things

196
00:18:25,770 --> 00:18:26,270
OK

197
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:34,040
Have a sit

198
00:18:42,870 --> 00:18:45,060
I used to be able to run for circles

199
00:18:45,540 --> 00:18:47,900
Now my legs hurt for taking a walk

200
00:18:51,540 --> 00:18:54,420
Uncle, I heard that there’s something with your heart

201
00:18:54,860 --> 00:18:56,110
Please take good care of yourself

202
00:18:58,650 --> 00:19:02,760
I know Yezi’s been busy lately

203
00:19:03,510 --> 00:19:09,380
Zhuxuan told me you are working on a program together

204
00:19:10,920 --> 00:19:12,540
It’s her old animations

205
00:19:13,280 --> 00:19:15,040
And I’m in charging of recomposing

206
00:19:15,990 --> 00:19:17,820
So we are co-charging this program

207
00:19:19,700 --> 00:19:21,910
We didn’t meet much

208
00:19:22,480 --> 00:19:24,040
But I’ve heard many things about you

209
00:19:27,690 --> 00:19:29,550
I believe in my daughter

210
00:19:30,980 --> 00:19:33,650
I never question her choices

211
00:19:35,130 --> 00:19:37,010
But I'm her father

212
00:19:38,080 --> 00:19:39,140
I can't help worrying about her

213
00:19:40,150 --> 00:19:42,390
Her mom and I are getting old

214
00:19:42,590 --> 00:19:44,290
We want her to have a good man

215
00:19:47,280 --> 00:19:48,390
So I want to ask you

216
00:19:49,180 --> 00:19:51,510
what’s going on with you and Yezi?

217
00:19:55,010 --> 00:19:56,160
Uncle, I totally understand you

218
00:19:58,340 --> 00:20:01,700
Like you, I also want Yezi to be happy

219
00:20:05,620 --> 00:20:06,310
To be honest

220
00:20:08,060 --> 00:20:16,910
Parents wish for nothing but a happy life for their kid

221
00:20:23,510 --> 00:20:30,350
So I am striving to give Yezi a life that she wants

222
00:20:34,600 --> 00:20:38,450
Do you really know what kind of life Yezi wants?

223
00:20:41,630 --> 00:20:45,530
You young people may think many of our ideas are outdated

224
00:20:46,170 --> 00:20:48,490
That I don't deny

225
00:20:48,960 --> 00:20:50,910
But what’s true is always true

226
00:20:52,210 --> 00:20:58,830
What every woman is looking for simply is accompany

227
00:21:01,930 --> 00:21:09,860
Some young people say that they prefer to cry in a BMW rather than smile on a bike

228
00:21:12,300 --> 00:21:20,200
But it’s not about the vehicle but the driver

229
00:21:24,210 --> 00:21:25,500
Uncle, I understand

230
00:21:26,450 --> 00:21:30,830
But do you think I can be that driver?

231
00:21:34,840 --> 00:21:41,920
You said that you are like me, wanting Yezi to be happy

232
00:21:43,600 --> 00:21:49,620
But what Yezi needs is more than a man that gives her happiness

233
00:21:50,090 --> 00:21:55,770
but a man that really knows what kind of happiness she wants

234
00:21:58,610 --> 00:22:00,190
If you really figure that out

235
00:22:01,480 --> 00:22:03,490
Our conversation today is pretty successful

236
00:22:07,270 --> 00:22:07,900
Forward, forward

237
00:22:08,320 --> 00:22:10,510
And I’m out

238
00:22:10,540 --> 00:22:12,300
Not yet

239
00:22:14,170 --> 00:22:15,510
Careful, mind the steps

240
00:22:17,160 --> 00:22:21,050
Honey, keep your eyes shut

241
00:22:23,760 --> 00:22:24,650
OK

242
00:22:25,260 --> 00:22:27,250
Wait, I'll count to three and on three you open your eyes
My eyes are closed

243
00:22:33,010 --> 00:22:35,820
1 2 3

244
00:22:38,740 --> 00:22:40,390
-Surprise  -Honey!

245
00:22:42,360 --> 00:22:44,270
Surprise, as promised

246
00:23:04,430 --> 00:23:05,280
Enjoy

247
00:23:09,890 --> 00:23:13,840
When I was preparing this

248
00:23:15,410 --> 00:23:20,380
It came to my mind that it’s not only a home for us

249
00:23:21,510 --> 00:23:24,370
But also a place that witnesses miracle

250
00:23:26,420 --> 00:23:27,970
You may not know

251
00:23:29,310 --> 00:23:30,560
Before I met you

252
00:23:31,650 --> 00:23:38,690
I thought I was a man of no romance but only knew corpses and cases

253
00:23:39,530 --> 00:23:50,010
I never imagined that I could marry a perfect wife and have a sweet home

254
00:23:52,220 --> 00:23:58,520
Honey, you gave me a second life

255
00:24:00,420 --> 00:24:01,260
you gave new meaning to my life

256
00:24:05,140 --> 00:24:09,020
You complain of how I am busy with work

257
00:24:11,330 --> 00:24:14,410
And how I don’t share my work life with you

258
00:24:15,270 --> 00:24:22,030
That’s because during work I see the dark side of human being a lot

259
00:24:22,870 --> 00:24:23,980
And I don’t want to share that with you

260
00:24:27,030 --> 00:24:30,520
That’s because since the first time we met

261
00:24:32,430 --> 00:24:35,830
I want offer you nothing but only good things

262
00:24:39,940 --> 00:24:42,470
When I see you working hard

263
00:24:44,400 --> 00:24:47,660
While I complain that you can’t fit into my life more

264
00:24:48,890 --> 00:24:49,840
I feel very guilty

265
00:24:52,030 --> 00:24:57,360
But honey, you are already in my life

266
00:24:58,760 --> 00:25:00,380
And you are the most important part of it

267
00:25:08,960 --> 00:25:09,740
Honey

268
00:25:13,020 --> 00:25:13,690
Honey

269
00:25:20,510 --> 00:25:22,310
Honey, it’s raining

270
00:25:23,750 --> 00:25:25,520
Why don’t we go in?

271
00:25:29,470 --> 00:25:31,420
No, it’s more romantic out here

272
00:25:34,050 --> 00:25:34,550
OK

273
00:25:35,300 --> 00:25:37,790
I’ll move the desk over here

274
00:25:38,260 --> 00:25:40,370
OK, you carry this one and I carry that one

275
00:26:12,300 --> 00:26:15,730
Xi, I have something to tell you

276
00:26:16,520 --> 00:26:17,030
What’s wrong?

277
00:26:21,620 --> 00:26:22,190
Take this

278
00:26:41,360 --> 00:26:42,220
You are going to Paris

279
00:26:46,360 --> 00:26:49,460
I’ve been thinking for a while and I decide to tell you today

280
00:26:50,030 --> 00:26:51,060
I don’t know how to break it to you

281
00:26:53,030 --> 00:26:54,290
I’ve been applying for this school for three years

282
00:26:56,050 --> 00:26:58,240
And I finally received their offer

283
00:26:59,910 --> 00:27:01,490
I haven’t replied yet

284
00:27:03,920 --> 00:27:04,530
What’s wrong?

285
00:27:12,390 --> 00:27:12,890
Wu Kai

286
00:27:18,120 --> 00:27:19,000
I’m breaking up with you

287
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:22,900
Xi

288
00:27:22,940 --> 00:27:24,860
Let go of me

289
00:27:24,940 --> 00:27:25,940
Listen to me

290
00:27:27,050 --> 00:27:28,630
I know what you are thinking

291
00:27:28,720 --> 00:27:30,470
I want to give you a future

292
00:27:31,210 --> 00:27:32,890
So please don’t go and listen to me

293
00:27:33,980 --> 00:27:35,390
Listen to me

294
00:27:51,530 --> 00:27:52,030
I know

295
00:27:53,850 --> 00:27:55,580
It’s unfair to you

296
00:27:57,490 --> 00:28:01,690
But I won't go as long as you ask me not to

297
00:28:09,160 --> 00:28:09,810
I’ve thought it through

298
00:28:10,360 --> 00:28:17,030
I can also stay in the country and open my own studio

299
00:28:18,090 --> 00:28:21,740
All I want is to build a future for us

300
00:28:30,690 --> 00:28:34,730
If I ask you to stay, you will stay

301
00:28:36,490 --> 00:28:37,190
Of course

302
00:28:37,580 --> 00:28:39,530
Do you think I’d choose a paper over you?

303
00:28:46,860 --> 00:28:47,710
How long will you be gone?

304
00:28:49,990 --> 00:28:50,490
One year

305
00:28:55,780 --> 00:29:00,560
Promise me you'll come back after one year

306
00:29:05,660 --> 00:29:06,290
Is it a yes?

307
00:29:09,050 --> 00:29:13,580
I promise I’ll come back in one year, not one second longer

308
00:29:19,080 --> 00:29:19,960
Xi, thank you

309
00:29:24,070 --> 00:29:27,510
Congratulations, Liu, on finally not being single anymore

310
00:29:30,900 --> 00:29:33,960
Now it turns to someone

311
00:29:38,010 --> 00:29:40,110
Traveling wedding ceremony, that’s fashionable.

312
00:29:40,310 --> 00:29:41,440
Didn’t your families say anything?

313
00:29:42,280 --> 00:29:46,250
It’s our wedding, our style

314
00:29:47,290 --> 00:29:51,650
No. He only told her parents about the game

315
00:29:52,850 --> 00:29:54,960
You already have an excuse to lose that game

316
00:29:56,040 --> 00:29:59,300
Someone can only think about wife but not game

317
00:30:00,590 --> 00:30:05,270
People, I only lost once, cut it out

318
00:30:05,530 --> 00:30:07,450
Look at Yu Lang, he didn’t say anything sarcastic

319
00:30:07,480 --> 00:30:08,250
Right, here, honey

320
00:30:09,370 --> 00:30:12,280
You can only have one thing between love and work

321
00:30:14,060 --> 00:30:16,110
I’m punching someone now, don’t hold me

322
00:30:16,610 --> 00:30:18,740
Don’t pick on my husband. Liu, control him

323
00:30:18,840 --> 00:30:19,660
Cut it out you all

324
00:30:19,830 --> 00:30:21,220
Come and see the gifts I bought

325
00:30:21,780 --> 00:30:22,520
You got me gifts?

326
00:30:22,780 --> 00:30:24,400
Liu, you are so nice

327
00:30:24,660 --> 00:30:26,270
Xinran is not stingy as you

328
00:30:26,280 --> 00:30:28,690
What did you say? Come, honey

329
00:30:29,270 --> 00:30:31,570
You took a lot of food from us back in college

330
00:30:31,600 --> 00:30:34,270
No, you gave food to me because I was adorable

331
00:30:38,380 --> 00:30:39,580
What?

332
00:30:41,020 --> 00:30:43,390
Did my marriage give you some thoughts?

333
00:30:45,320 --> 00:30:46,210
Not really

334
00:30:47,940 --> 00:30:51,540
I mean, aren’t you planning on taking one more step?

335
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:58,490
I used to think getting married is going to jail

336
00:31:00,390 --> 00:31:03,330
But now when I actually do it I find that

337
00:31:04,270 --> 00:31:05,280
Marriage can also be heaven

338
00:31:11,990 --> 00:31:15,680
I never thought that you’d marry earlier than I do

339
00:31:19,070 --> 00:31:23,940
Marriage can make a man grow up

340
00:31:25,010 --> 00:31:29,510
I used to be, I know, a little bit childish

341
00:31:29,990 --> 00:31:34,070
But being with Xinran has taught me a lot

342
00:31:35,440 --> 00:31:42,050
These girls, as we all know, appear to be strong

343
00:31:43,390 --> 00:31:46,640
But they all need a strong shoulder to rely on

344
00:32:09,690 --> 00:32:10,440
What is happiness?

345
00:32:14,320 --> 00:32:19,200
I didn’t know how to answer this question before I met her

346
00:32:21,860 --> 00:32:28,220
But since I met her, happiness is no longer a question to me

347
00:32:31,320 --> 00:32:34,800
My happiness became simple and pure

348
00:32:42,410 --> 00:32:43,220
I want a home

349
00:32:45,920 --> 00:32:47,240
A home that belongs to the two of us

350
00:32:49,240 --> 00:32:49,820
Dinner time

351
00:32:51,300 --> 00:32:52,300
Like this

352
00:32:55,340 --> 00:32:55,850
Dinner

353
00:32:55,860 --> 00:32:56,850
Come and have dinner

354
00:32:56,860 --> 00:32:57,610
Let's eat!

355
00:32:57,820 --> 00:33:02,050
Have a taste, I made this

356
00:33:02,500 --> 00:33:04,250
Much meat today

357
00:33:04,340 --> 00:33:06,450
Look at those meat

358
00:33:06,460 --> 00:33:07,090
You have some too

359
00:33:07,100 --> 00:33:07,650
OK

360
00:33:07,660 --> 00:33:08,930
Here, have some of these

361
00:33:08,940 --> 00:33:09,730
Let me

362
00:33:09,740 --> 00:33:10,330
Here's your meat

363
00:33:10,340 --> 00:33:11,090
You first

364
00:33:12,780 --> 00:33:13,770
Look at them, isn't that sweet?

365
00:33:18,140 --> 00:33:19,050
You have some

366
00:33:19,940 --> 00:33:21,610
You too

367
00:33:21,860 --> 00:33:23,090
Well, thank you

368
00:33:23,660 --> 00:33:24,930
This is for you
Thanks

369
00:33:25,740 --> 00:33:27,730
Let me do that

370
00:33:28,980 --> 00:33:29,780
What is home?

371
00:33:33,430 --> 00:33:35,520
I didn't quite understand the meaning of that word when I was little

372
00:33:36,780 --> 00:33:38,820
I thought home meant  a big house

373
00:33:41,090 --> 00:33:43,200
When I finished my homework

374
00:33:43,830 --> 00:33:46,250
I’d lean on windows and wait for my parents to come back

375
00:33:48,600 --> 00:33:54,770
My father used to flash his light when he drove near our house

376
00:33:55,650 --> 00:34:00,540
So that I’d been waken up if I fell asleep in front of windows

377
00:34:02,540 --> 00:34:05,760
So that I’d know that they were back and I could go to bed

378
00:34:08,880 --> 00:34:13,210
I remember that every night when my dad went back he'd came to my room

379
00:34:14,660 --> 00:34:15,800
He thought I was sleeping

380
00:34:17,410 --> 00:34:21,390
And there were many times that I hided in bed with my shoes on

381
00:34:21,960 --> 00:34:24,500
Because I worried that they found out I stayed up waiting for them

382
00:34:25,670 --> 00:34:26,930
But he never found out

383
00:34:33,130 --> 00:34:38,830
Maybe expecting that flash is what home meant to me

384
00:34:40,720 --> 00:34:45,380
Until one day, I came here

385
00:35:38,890 --> 00:35:40,140
Being a painter sounds pretty good

386
00:35:41,300 --> 00:35:44,030
And I think you can make it because you are very talented

387
00:35:45,120 --> 00:35:48,170
Of course I can make it

388
00:35:51,000 --> 00:35:54,550
I will publish your animations when you become a real painter

389
00:35:57,420 --> 00:35:59,300
Anything you want, you name it

390
00:35:59,510 --> 00:36:00,100
Really?

391
00:36:00,450 --> 00:36:03,060
Sure, you can count on me, your big brother Lin Sen

392
00:36:03,900 --> 00:36:06,570
I called you big brother when we were kids

393
00:36:07,170 --> 00:36:09,160
From now on I'll call you by your name

394
00:36:19,820 --> 00:36:20,890
On one condition

395
00:36:21,850 --> 00:36:22,380
What condition?

396
00:36:23,840 --> 00:36:25,310
Give that painting to me when you finish it

397
00:36:27,540 --> 00:36:28,040
Fine

398
00:36:34,170 --> 00:36:35,840
What do you want to do in future?

399
00:36:36,670 --> 00:36:37,830
Definitely to be a doctor

400
00:36:38,190 --> 00:36:39,510
Why a doctor?

401
00:36:40,900 --> 00:36:45,740
So that I can take care of those who matter to me and make them healthy and happy forever

402
00:37:02,050 --> 00:37:02,550
Are you alright?

403
00:37:05,480 --> 00:37:06,110
What are you doing here?

404
00:37:09,650 --> 00:37:13,120
Here this is brown sugar and this is ginger tea

405
00:37:13,210 --> 00:37:14,220
Drink some when you feel painful

406
00:37:15,500 --> 00:37:17,910
This is warm pads, remember to use them

407
00:37:18,460 --> 00:37:20,920
Painkillers, eat them when you really can’t hold it

408
00:37:20,940 --> 00:37:23,520
They are not good for health, OK?

409
00:37:27,720 --> 00:37:29,830
I’m late for class. Call me if you need me

410
00:37:29,860 --> 00:37:30,780
OK, thank you

411
00:37:36,680 --> 00:37:39,910
Take painkillers only when you can’t hold it

412
00:38:08,640 --> 00:38:11,180
-Mrs Yu ,can I borrow you one minute? -Who are you?

413
00:38:11,790 --> 00:38:14,500
These are painted by a friend of mine, she really wants to work with your press

414
00:38:14,520 --> 00:38:15,100
Please take a look

415
00:38:15,120 --> 00:38:16,000
Sorry, I’m busy

416
00:38:16,030 --> 00:38:17,480
Just one look, Mrs Yu

417
00:38:18,320 --> 00:38:18,870
One look

418
00:38:28,240 --> 00:38:29,220
All these are her work?

419
00:38:29,270 --> 00:38:30,880
Yes, she is very talented

420
00:38:32,650 --> 00:38:35,640
-Yezi -Yes, she just graduated from art school

421
00:38:36,430 --> 00:38:38,260
I’ll contact her

422
00:38:38,440 --> 00:38:39,810
I promise

423
00:38:40,500 --> 00:38:41,000
Thank you

424
00:38:46,790 --> 00:38:47,570
Price doesn’t matter

425
00:38:47,890 --> 00:38:48,390
OK

426
00:38:57,190 --> 00:39:01,150
Mr Xiao, I need a clapboard over there

427
00:39:01,470 --> 00:39:04,490
I’m building the main showroom here, please set it up for me

428
00:39:04,630 --> 00:39:05,280
I will

429
00:39:35,240 --> 00:39:35,740
No

430
00:39:36,170 --> 00:39:36,670
Zhuxuan

431
00:39:37,240 --> 00:39:38,070
You are here, Lin Sen

432
00:39:39,840 --> 00:39:40,450
Let me help

433
00:39:42,570 --> 00:39:43,640
I can use some help

434
00:39:45,120 --> 00:39:46,100
How is this place?

435
00:39:48,790 --> 00:39:49,890
Why are you giggling?

436
00:39:51,180 --> 00:39:52,910
-It’s finally over,and I’m happy

437
00:39:54,650 --> 00:39:58,590
Lin Sen, you did so many things for Yezi and never told her

438
00:39:58,710 --> 00:39:59,830
Worth it?

439
00:40:00,960 --> 00:40:05,550
You were the one who found the place for our new office

440
00:40:06,470 --> 00:40:07,420
You were the one hiring the workers

441
00:40:09,040 --> 00:40:12,070
You were the one handling the exhibition

442
00:40:13,970 --> 00:40:16,680
You chose and sent these planets here

443
00:40:17,180 --> 00:40:19,150
But Yezi knows nothing about all of these things

444
00:40:19,270 --> 00:40:22,080
It's such a sacrifice to be a anonymous hero

445
00:40:23,560 --> 00:40:24,890
You said anonymous yourself

446
00:40:25,380 --> 00:40:26,310
And it’s really nothing to mention

447
00:40:27,060 --> 00:40:29,740
It’s everything

448
00:40:29,740 --> 00:40:30,360
Fine

449
00:40:32,740 --> 00:40:36,960
I've been used to it since I was a kid

450
00:40:41,070 --> 00:40:42,520
You are stubborn like Yezi

451
00:41:12,940 --> 00:41:14,890
You just woke up, take good rest

452
00:41:20,340 --> 00:41:22,220
Yu, what are you doing here?

453
00:41:23,570 --> 00:41:25,540
We heard Yishan woke up so we are here to visit

454
00:41:29,240 --> 00:41:33,420
Yishan, you have visitors, why don’t you say hi?

455
00:41:39,210 --> 00:41:39,710
Sit please

456
00:41:44,590 --> 00:41:48,130
Sorry, he is still recovering and don't like to talk

457
00:41:52,330 --> 00:41:53,160
Give us some privacy

458
00:41:58,960 --> 00:42:00,510
Are you taking those little things to visit a patient?

459
00:42:04,440 --> 00:42:12,690
Yu, my uncle told me that you are the chief editor now

460
00:42:14,690 --> 00:42:16,020
Have you already forgotten where you came from?

461
00:42:19,450 --> 00:42:25,030
If it wasn’t for my animations, can you make it here?

462
00:42:26,140 --> 00:42:30,700
Gu Yishan, cut it out already, was it your animations?

463
00:42:35,070 --> 00:42:36,520
Of course it’s mine

464
00:42:38,120 --> 00:42:39,740
I painted them all

465
00:42:40,300 --> 00:42:44,710
Can't you see my name on it? Can't you?

466
00:42:47,000 --> 00:42:52,160
Yishan just came to himself, let’s stop fighting

467
00:43:00,860 --> 00:43:07,400
By the way, Yishan, what was really going on with that animation?

468
00:43:08,700 --> 00:43:13,610
Why, are you suspecting me too?

469
00:43:15,340 --> 00:43:21,130
What’s wrong with you people?

470
00:43:22,150 --> 00:43:24,750
Who do you think painted that animation but me?

471
00:43:26,590 --> 00:43:27,320
Xiang Zeyi?

472
00:43:30,980 --> 00:43:33,770
Was he the only capable one?

473
00:43:35,260 --> 00:43:40,430
I’m telling you, I am the real and the only painter

474
00:43:42,420 --> 00:43:46,600
And Xiang Zeyi was not a good student of art school long ago

475
00:43:47,530 --> 00:43:52,090
He is nothing but an offender under labour reform

476
00:43:55,770 --> 00:43:57,540
Uncle, my head hurts

477
00:43:58,690 --> 00:44:00,720
OK, have some rest then

478
00:44:03,980 --> 00:44:04,890
Look at yourself

479
00:44:07,500 --> 00:44:10,730
Uncle, I just feel so wronged

480
00:44:13,000 --> 00:44:15,430
No one believes I was the painter

481
00:44:20,090 --> 00:44:20,860
Don’t think too much

482
00:44:22,430 --> 00:44:23,040
I believe you

483
00:44:24,560 --> 00:44:25,660
You must believe me

484
00:44:26,800 --> 00:44:27,800
Your nephew’s life is really hard

485
00:44:30,270 --> 00:44:30,980
I know
